  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "How can I retrieve my WeChat account if I've forgotten my password, I just linked my linked & I remember I wechat ID.But I don't have QQ/phone linked?",
  "response": "If you've forgotten your WeChat password and don't have a linked QQ account or phone number, you can still try to recover your account through several methods. Here\u2019s a step-by-step guide:\n\n### Option 1: Recover via Email (If you linked an email)\n1. **Open WeChat**: Launch the WeChat app on your device.\n2. **Tap on \"Forgot Password?\"**: This should be on the login screen.\n3. **Select \"Linked Email Address\"**: Follow the prompts to reset your password using the linked email.\n\n### Option 2: Account Recovery via WeChat ID\n1. **Open WeChat**: Go to the WeChat app.\n2. **Tap on \"Forgot Password?\"**: Found on the login screen.\n3. **Select \"Log in via WeChat ID\"**: Enter your WeChat ID that you remember.\n5. **Follow the instructions**: You may need to prove your identity through associated security verifications.\n\n### Option 3: Contact WeChat Support\n1. **Visit the WeChat Help Center**: Go to WeChat\u2019s official help center at [WeChat Help Center](https://help.wechat.com).\n2. **Submit a request**: Look for \u201cCan\u2019t log in\u201d or similar options, and fill in the required information explaining your situation.\n3. **Provide details**: You might need to provide your WeChat ID, the approximate date of account creation, and any other relevant information that can help verify your identity.\n4. **Wait for a response**: WeChat support will review your case and help you with the recovery process.\n\n### Option 4: Using a Friend\u2019s Help\n1. **Contact a WeChat friend**: Ask a friend who is already connected with you on WeChat to use the \u201cHelp Friend Log In\u201d feature.\n2. **Follow Instructions**: Your friend can assist by verifying your account through their WeChat, which might help establish your identity.\n\nRemember to check if any recovery email or notification has been sent to your previously linked email or contact support directly for detailed assistance.\n\n### Additional Tips:\n- Always keep your account information updated with linked email or phone for recovery options.\n- Use strong, memorable passwords and store them securely.\n\nIf none of these options work, contacting WeChat support directly will be your best shot at recovering your account.",
